description: This data comes from the American Fitness Index Report. It includes data for New Orleans MSA and several benchmark MSAs including: Atlanta, Baton Rouge, Louisville, Memphis, Miami, Nashville/Davidson, Oklahoma City, Raleigh, and Tampa. The data is published annually beginning in 2010.
